f edges, for all choices of parameters.\n  Finally, we provide some applications of our results to approximate shortest\npaths' computation in unweighted graphs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jul 2016 07:47:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Feb 2017 13:00:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-07"}
