k is the first deep hashing method that can perform hash\ncode learning and feature learning simultaneously in a semi-supervised fashion.\nExperimental results on 5 widely-used datasets show that our proposed approach\noutperforms the state-of-the-art hashing methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jul 2016 14:30:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 18 Jun 2017 07:52:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2017 03:23:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-08"}
